# Base URL of the deployed MANARA FastAPI backend, with no path suffix
# (the client appends /query itself). Leave unset for local development —
# the Vite dev server proxies /api to http://127.0.0.1:8000 automatically
# (see vite.config.ts), which avoids CORS without any backend changes.
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://your-manara-api.example.com
